{"word":"G283 - ἀμίαντος - amíantos - am-ee'-an-tos - Undefiled","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἀμίαντος</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">amíantos</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">am-ee'-an-tos</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Undefiled</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adjective / பெயரடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"மாசில்லாத, அசுசிப்படாத, மாசற்ற - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":"not defiled, unsoiled, free from that by which the nature of a thing is deformed and debased, its force and vigor impaired"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G1 - Α - A - al'-fah/1\">G1</a> (as a negative particle) and a derivative of <a href=\"#/G3392 - μιαίνω - miaínō - me-ah'-ee-no/3392\">G3392</a>; <i>unsoiled</i>, that is, (figuratively) <i>pure:</i> - undefiled.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G283/283\">G283</a>, <a href=\"#/G3392/3392\">G3392</a>, <a href=\"#/G3393/3393\">G3393</a>, <a href=\"#/G3394/3394\">G3394</a>"}]}